Package: RCamelsPE
Type: Package
Title: Access, Process, and Visualize CAMELS-PE Data
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    person(
        given = "Harold",
        family = "Llauca",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "hllauca@senamhi.gob.pe"
    )
Description: Provides tools to read, process, and visualize hydrological,
    climatic, physiographic, and geospatial data from the CAMELS-PE dataset
    (Catchment Attributes and Meteorology for Large-sample Studies - Peru).
    The package is designed to work with externally stored CAMELS-PE data and
    does not include the dataset itself. Functions support reading daily time
    series, catchment attributes, station metadata, metadata dictionaries, and
    geospatial layers, as well as basic visualization of time series and
    catchment boundaries.
